<hr>
<strong>WORKS CITED</strong>
<br><br>
Add a &#8216;Works Cited&#8217; entry at the end of your essay citing all sources used in the body of your writing.
<br><br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	&#34;Title of article.&#34; <em>Name of Journal</em>, volume, issue, year of publication, page numbers.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent">
	&#34;<span class="hover" title="Title of article">Study Smarter, Not Harder: Setting Goals to Improve Your Academic Performance</span>.&#34; 
	<em><span class="hover" title="Name of Journal">Student Review</span></em>,
	<span class="hover" title="volume">vol. 25</span>, <span class="hover" title="issue">no. 5</span>,
	<span class="hover" title="year of publication">2056</span>, 
	<span class="hover" title="page numbers">pp. 10&#45;12</span>.
</blockquote>
<br>
